		<title>Measure a machine’s heart</title>
		<link>/work/measure-a-machines-heart/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[baoanhbui]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 03:42:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">/?post_type=work#038;p=96</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[In this project, I gave a machine a kind of human-like passion and showed how that passion either ramps up (lights up) or fades away (burns out) depending on a few factors. The visual style is reminiscent of the data you see on an ECG machine, and all of that can be explored within the [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">
<html><body><p>In this project, I gave a machine a kind of human-like passion and showed how that passion either ramps up (lights up) or fades away (burns out) depending on a few factors. The visual style is reminiscent of the data you see on an ECG machine, and all of that can be explored within the developer tools.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Visit the site here <a href="https://vanghoa.github.io/bonghoanho/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">vanghoa.github.io/bonghoanho/</a>.</li>



<li>Take a look at the <a href="https://github.com/vanghoa/bonghoanho" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">github repository</a>.</li>
</ul>



<figure class="wp-block-image" style="--width:1846; --height:1846;"><img decoding="async" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/djtuan5jn/image/upload/v1715840752/personalwebsite/image/978f1cb9-e997-4fad-872a-0d3fde58cb00/aanymcinlpqhpgwopmmt.png" alt="cover.png" width="1846" height="1846" fetchpriority="high"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image thumb" style="--width:2000; --height:2000;"><img decoding="async" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/djtuan5jn/image/upload/v1715840757/personalwebsite/image/978f1cb9-e997-4fad-872a-0d3fde58cb00/uruhfqvipj0ykrnwj3a9.png" alt="remote.png" width="2000" height="2000" fetchpriority="high"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo span2"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:960; --height:559;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:960; --theight:559;" alt="thumbnail" src="" data-src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1799684035-8e7e99070dbdc0410d6d2faf5ac156e256db8d5318ab223b832ecab2ba0fb752-d_960" data-srcset="" srcset=""><iframe title="Measure a machine's heart v5" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/913716080?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>Visualizing in the Styles panel</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:960; --height:960;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:960; --theight:960;" alt="thumbnail" src="" data-src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1736702905-520debb549a8ccb629fcdf6e0922d7fa41efa3f7fbdaf4d2c1aa22ec1b916e05-d_960" data-srcset="" srcset=""><iframe title="Measure a machine's heart &ndash; CSS" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/873271271?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>Visualizing in the Console panel</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo span3"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:960; --height:296;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:960; --theight:296;" alt="thumbnail" src="" data-src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1738618833-5412c0f6ec206f560029226177f49c082e759fea1bf5bfe8d7afd263be38c871-d_960" data-srcset="" srcset=""><iframe title="Measure a machine's heart &ndash; console" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/874515036?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>Visualizing camera projection into ASCII art and microphone recording into the remote size&nbsp;(viewed inside the &lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt; tag), this was added when I tried to improve this project as a submission to HTML Review 2024</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo span2"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:960; --height:559;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:960; --theight:559;" alt="thumbnail" src="" data-src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1799683082-a04062927652e14debe533fb8f4e2c03b876b99ea0cda46c713e7deed365efe7-d_960" data-srcset="" srcset=""><iframe title="Measure a machine's heart &ndash; eyes &amp; ears v4" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/913715996?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Thank you T&#432;&#7901;ng Vi Ng for reaching out to me for showing it at the B&ocirc;ng Hoa Nh&#7887; exhibition 2023 by B&#7855;p X&agrave;o</li>



<li>Thank you Max &amp; Shelby for allowing me to show and improve this work on HTML Review 2024.</li>
</ul>
</body></html>
