					<description><![CDATA[This marked my first time developing a website entirely from scratch, without the use of plugins or web-building tools. I hand-coded the site using only plain HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript, then slapped it up on Github Pages as a static website. All that stuff I&#8217;d been accumulating from my past projects, from Semplice, from [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">
<html><body><ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Visit the <a href="https://vanghoa.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">vanghoa.github.io</a> to see the website.</li>



<li>Take a look at the <a href="https://github.com/vanghoa/vanghoa.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">github repository</a>.</li>
</ul>



<p>This marked my first time developing a website entirely from scratch, without the use of plugins or web-building tools. I hand-coded the site using only plain HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript, then slapped it up on Github Pages as a static website. </p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo span2 row2"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:960; --height:605;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:960; --theight:605;" alt="thumbnail" src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1736646038-5d085810070592ddadea6ef89eca2828ab3a515c14518d2cd926f57ec64ea67d-d_960" fetchpriority="high"><iframe title="Personal website 2022" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/873233426?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>All that stuff I&rsquo;d been accumulating from my past projects, from Semplice, from Webflow, from Javascriptinfo and more, it all clicked into place. This experience was like connecting the dots and seeing my knowledge come to life. Plus, it wasn&rsquo;t just about making sense of what I already knew &ndash; I got to build more on top of it during the process. Amazing!</p>



