										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">
<html><body><ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Visit the <a href="https://vanghoa.github.io/vlog-template/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">vanghoa.github.io/vlog-template/</a> to see the website.</li>



<li>Take a look at the <a href="https://github.com/vanghoa/vlog-template" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">github repository</a>.</li>
</ul>



<p>The concept of the &ldquo;navigation bar in the middle of nowhere&rdquo; had been on my checklist for a while. It could be seen as an additional meaning layer on top of the navigation bar surrounding the four sides on my previous &lsquo;Personal website 2022&rsquo;.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo span2"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:892; --height:892;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:640; --theight:640;" alt="thumbnail" src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1736687486-79fada06518ca8775b4b3b7a5b21f4c4821c895a780832b53d6dac110fe820ed-d_640" fetchpriority="high"><iframe title="The navigation bar that is in the middle of nowhere" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/873260364?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>Initially, the website&rsquo;s objective is to archive all of my video footages and images during my internship at Practice Theory. The idea was to use the site as a presentation platform for my vlogs, where I would screen record and narrate them using my voice. It was a convenient way to showcase my experiences and work on a weekly basis.</p>



